copy_image_to_clipboard.current_docstring:
Copies an image to the system clipboard

EXAMPLE:

    >>> ans = get_youtube_video_thumbnail('https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iu54gTucsiE')
    ... copy_image_to_clipboard(ans)
